description: Martin is searching for the entrance portal to a parallel dimension inhabited by fairies and goblins in order to restore the Triskelion , a magical object of unknown nature . After various vicissitudes , a member of the Little People , indicates the way to to Martin : The detective discovers that the next stage of his research will be the Lake Maggiore in Italy . But to get there, he must first deal with a terrible demon ...
name: Il regno delle fate

description:
The origin of Desertwind is revealed in this action packed and thought-provoking collection.

Christian Superheroes: Desertwind - The Origin of Desertwind, the super-speedster must make some tough choices about his life and faith. Christian Superheroes: Desertwind is 20 pages w/full color cover and b/w interior art. Published by Christian Knight Comics Group.
name: The Origin of Desertwind

description: A supernatural presence watches over Martin and Java who, in the course of their research of the door to enter the Kingdom of the Fairies, must deal with demonic entities and the "Men in Black". Their investigation leads them from Ireland to Lake Maggiore, and there, under the Rock of Angera, they find the passage that brings them to the sight of Oberon and Titania, rulers of the Fairyland.
name: La Signora del Lago

description: A ruthless murder kicks off a dark story which combines magic and advanced technology. Martin Mystere and Java are involved and, in a secret laboratory at the Polytechnic of Milan, the detective of the impossible has to a duel in a fantasy world recreated by virtual reality. An imaginary duel, but the effects, if he loses, are dangerously real.
name: I prigionieri del ciberspazio

description: A diabolical plot that has already caused dozens of deaths will endanger the life of the Pope and the very existence of the Earth! Martin Mystere and Java they are made aware by Jaspar, the omniscent guy that can access the ‚Äúuniversal databank". Jaspar ha s grown and seems to have lost his cool detachment from the world, perhaps because the Earth could soon be destroyed by the advent of the Antichrist
name: Il ritorno di Jaspar

description:
In a new tale from classic 1970s writer Cary Bates, Gorilla Grodd unleashes his most ruthless attack yet against his nemesis, The Flash ‚Äì a plan for revenge so warped and diabolical, it dooms The Scarlet Speedster to a slow and agonizing fate that will end his heroic career and cause an unspeakable rift between Barry and his wife, Iris!

Plus: Following the 26-page lead story is a classic tale originally published in the '70s, also written by Cary Bates!

Notes:

  • Reprints DC Comics Presents #2.
name: Son of Grodd / Race to the End of Time!

description:
From legendary scribe Dennis O'Neil comes an untold adventure starring DC's Amazon Princess in her "white costume" phase! When Paradise Island is in danger, Wonder Woman must complete three tasks to save her homeland from destruction. But are these tasks too difficult even for her?

Plus: Following the 26-page lead story is a classic tale originally published in the '70s, also written by Dennis O'Neil!
name: Savage Ritual; The Fist of Flame

description:
The 1970s was a pivotal decade for Batman, one in which he transitioned from TV's campy Caped Crusader into today's Dark Knight Detective!

Now, legendary scribe Len Wein (DC UNIVERSE: LEGACIES) tells a never-before-revealed tale from this era in a brand-new story!

Plus: Following the 26-page lead story is a classic tale originally published in the '70s, also written by Len Wein! [Batman #307]
name: Terror Times Three!; Dark Messenger of Mercy!
